---
layout: default
title: Eleventy Display GitHub Repositories
---

This page displays all of the repositories for the configured GitHub user account from <a href="https://github.com/johnwargo/github-repos-sample-unauthorized" target="_blank">Eleventy Display GitHub Repositories (no auth)</a>.

{% if collections.repositories.length > 0 %}
  <p>Number of Repositories: {{ collections.repositories.length }}</p>
  <ul>
  {% for repo in collections.repositories %}
    <li>   
      <a href="{{ repo.html_url }}" target="_blank">{{ repo.name }}</a>
      {% if repo.description.length > 0 %}
        {{ repo.description }}
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>  
{% else %}
  <p>No repository data to display</p>
{% endif %}
